{"id":121984,"date":"2021-07-27T11:05:19","date_gmt":"2021-07-27T11:05:19","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/?p=121984"},"modified":"2021-07-27T13:30:55","modified_gmt":"2021-07-27T13:30:55","slug":"financial-commission-announces-partnership-with-finwizard-to-help-members-in-their-hiring-needs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/2021\/07\/27\/financial-commission-announces-partnership-with-finwizard-to-help-members-in-their-hiring-needs\/","title":{"rendered":"Financial Commission Announces Partnership with Finwizard to Help Members\u2019 in Their Hiring Needs\u00a0","gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"text"}]},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">July 27th,\u00a0 2021, The Financial Commission today announces a partnership with <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/finwizard.org\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Finwizard<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> &#8211; a new HR consulting service specific to the online brokerage industry to help broker members find the right candidates for their hiring needs.\u00a0 The new Value-added service allows Financial Commission broker members to enjoy 50% off any fees for the first successful hire using Finwizard*!<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 120px;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/3.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-121912 size-medium\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/3-300x211.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"211\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/3-300x211.png 300w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/3-1024x721.png 1024w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/3-768x541.png 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/3-830x584.png 830w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/3-230x162.png 230w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/3-350x246.png 350w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/3-480x338.png 480w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/3.png 1142w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/a>\u00a0 \u00a0 <a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/2.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-121921 size-medium\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/2-300x243.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"243\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/2-300x243.png 300w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/2-768x623.png 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/2-830x673.png 830w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/2-230x186.png 230w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/2-350x284.png 350w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/2-480x389.png 480w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/2.png 972w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/a>\u00a0 \u00a0 <a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-121930 size-medium\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1-300x149.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"149\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1-300x149.png 300w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1-1024x507.png 1024w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1-768x381.png 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1-1536x761.png 1536w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1-830x411.png 830w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1-230x114.png 230w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1-350x173.png 350w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1-480x238.png 480w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1.png 1764w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><b>Finwizard Hiring Approach\u00a0<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/finwizard.org\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Finwizard<\/a> has over 15 years of experience in placing the most qualified people in brokerages from entry-level to executive positions. The company uses its unique approach by partnering with top brokers and connecting candidates with opportunities that will put their skills to work in exciting ways.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The HR consulting service maintains an extensive database of candidates for all departments and executive positions and is ready to provide consulting services to the human resources of any online brokerage.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><strong>Finwizard delivers:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Top Talent acquisition across the globe<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Professional initial screening interviews with candidates<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Role-specific test assignments<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Background &amp; reference check<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Getting the right people for your goals and company culture<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">No prepayments! Payment only after a successful hire;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Free replacements of candidates who do not pass probation;<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"fc-blue-button\" href=\"mailto:info@financialcommission.com.co?subject=FinWizard inquiry\"><button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-bl\" type=\"button\">REQUEST CANDIDATES<br \/>\nNOW<\/button><\/a><\/p>\n<p><b>About Financial Commission<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Financial Commission is an independent external dispute resolution (EDR) organization for consumers\/traders who are unable to resolve disputes directly with their financial services providers that are members of the Financial Commission. The Financial Commission initially set out to provide a new approach for traders and brokers alike to resolve any issues that arise in the course of trading electronic markets such as Foreign Exchange, and then expanded into CFDs and related derivatives, in addition to certifying technology platforms used for trading.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For more information please contact us at <\/span><a href=\"mailto:info@financialcommission.com.co\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">info@financialcommission.com.co<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0b6675;\">*The Finwizard service is provided with a 50% discount for any fees incurred during the successful first hire for broker members who are in good standing with the Commission per the Commission\u2019s Rules and Guidelines.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false,